{"tid":1016172,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"其實大家有乜資格插陳詠謙","createTime":"2019-02-10T15:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T07:46:43.000Z","uid":199570,"like":37,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"10f46a01920510a059aa616c60ef435d13216e6d","tid":1016172,"uid":199570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"我就唔明啦<br />\n就以佢首本名曲別來無恙為例啦<br />\n其實已經係2015年既作品啦<br />\n四年前既野點解當時無人講要依家攞返出黎講？<br />\n咪就係因為你地班香港人淨係識得跟風<br />\n見人踩自己又加多兩錢肉緊踩多兩腳<br />\n講到自己咁勁 當時你又唔講<br />\n依家先黎馬後炮 人講你又講 <br />\n仲分分鐘唔知邊度有問題<br />\n依家佢一有新詞就即刻衝出黎鬧佢<br />\n就算無問題都好 就攞返以前嗰啲黎數<br />\n見高拜見低踩<br />\n明明當時高山低谷同矛盾一生就係咁吹奏佢講中自己心聲又點點點<br />\n你地話佢囂 其實有一部分都係你地造成架啦<br />\n神又係你 鬼又係你 你地玩曬啦 遲早全部都比你地批鬥曬"},{"pid":"1d0fefc7d0510de744572dabb68ea5a4add3f861","tid":1016172,"uid":142313,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"連登係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你睇下其他地方邊個討論區好似連登咁癡線？"},{"pid":"c2c1212325cf4ae680b367ac5751da842b6b1394","tid":1016172,"uid":174432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"情人遊天地 日月換行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a1da2fbda41e9988e1e39a991127e0f30c31cd","tid":1016172,"uid":178584,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"個陣無人講 唔代表啲人唔覺得填得差"},{"pid":"51ecb21fbb414e8fc5c5dd345adbd4e3db9079cf","tid":1016172,"uid":94828,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"係囉六四都三十年前啦仲成日講"},{"pid":"e32203c55c39752189cc2d02e80bd318e0168e5f","tid":1016172,"uid":150100,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"都唔啲人仲講耶穌做乜<br />\n成幾千年前嘅事啦"},{"pid":"886d0a3de6515e7e4ebfd310b7c63ec4343cb13b","tid":1016172,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d0fefc7d0510de744572dabb68ea5a4add3f861","tid":1016172,"uid":142313,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"連登係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你睇下其他地方邊個討論區好似連登咁癡線？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:58:46.000Z","msg":"駁5刀"},{"pid":"f1357a85cdb257f7a23ab19ce92db364106b777e","tid":1016172,"uid":149877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"難怪佢身邊太多假人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72df192191d820f2433577341a6b4e4e6a01d0c2","tid":1016172,"uid":102609,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:16:12.000Z","msg":"高山低谷同矛盾一生出嗰陣<br />\n已經周圍同frd講係畀啲冇腦港女港男聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於你話別來無恙已經係幾年前<br />\n咁龍舌蘭都係幾個月前出啫<br />\n邊個話剩係屌一首歌咁少？<br />\n同埋做咗多年Eason fans<br />\n見到新碟歌詞畀晒陳詠謙寫<br />\n而且仲10首有八首都係垃圾詞<br />\n咁都唔畀屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a1a5bdc7b6559b0c810f21d046f8dd357083c9","tid":1016172,"uid":199138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f9987ffc5283557cc9fdeffe6f34459e9bc74c","tid":1016172,"uid":91263,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:47:06.000Z","msg":"其實佢好多歌詞係體會過既人先會明，例如拍拖時女朋友好鐘意同我煮飯仔，當時我好抗拒，覺得出去食未算，散左之後先開始鐘意自己煮飯，自己浪漫"},{"pid":"518fffafe6ed998197ae770237f2bae8bf39a1cc","tid":1016172,"uid":199570,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c2c1212325cf4ae680b367ac5751da842b6b1394","tid":1016172,"uid":174432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"情人遊天地 日月換行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"其實呢句好有意境 唔係9填<br />\n我一開始聽仲諗緊終於唔係陳詠謙填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bb92942a409077b1304c193b5ed89e1d8c77be","tid":1016172,"uid":163621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"別來無恙真係好好聽<br />\n而「我現時自己肯做飯」係神來之筆<br />\n多謝連登咁落力幫首歌宣傳<br />\n令更多人認識呢首好歌"},{"pid":"4115b9d54ecd7863e717b4e2ea496b753c6aa7ad","tid":1016172,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"矛盾一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd547b2a689c6c41d76bb01c8a433e7ae897848","tid":1016172,"uid":104210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"因為嗰時佢未上位 只係心諗竟然有人填啲咁嘅柒詞<br />\n但而家係慨嘆蜀中無大將 填到咁都拎叱咤 所以要屌"}]}